      "id": "surrender_inertia",
      "text": "Stop fighting it",
      "description": "Maybe you're just not meant to be productive.",
      "resultText": "You let go of the guilt and the expectations. Some people are doers; you're not one of them. You settle into passivity like a warm bath. Bills pile up, opportunities pass, but you tell yourself you're choosing a different path—one of acceptance, of being rather than doing. The immediate relief of dropping the burden is real, but so is the growing sense that you're disappearing into your own life.",
